    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 9. Reativar Agente v2.1 (Multi-Tenant)\n\nRemove automaticamente a etiqueta agente-off quando uma conversa e resolvida no Chatwoot.\n\nv2.1 FIXES:\n- Multi-tenant: busca chatwoot_url, account_id e telegram_chat_id da tabela tenants via inbox_id\n- Nenhum valor hardcoded - funciona para qualquer tenant ativo\n\nConfigurar webhook no Chatwoot:\nSettings > Integrations > Webhooks > adicionar URL abaixo\nSelecionar evento: conversation_status_changed\n\nURL do webhook (producao):\nhttps://n8n.singulare.org/webhook/chatwoot-conversa-resolvida",
        "height": 240,
        "width": 704,
        "color": 3
      },
